</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p ">Determines which ink is allowed, the region is written in the rfid tag on the ink bottle. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">0 = All 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">1 = USA 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">2 = EMEA 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">3 = ASIA. 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p ">Defaults to zero, then the first bottle that is used for filling sets the region. All next bottles must be of the same region. 
</p><note id="GUID-74F59052-4CA7-4AEC-974F-C37069B328F4" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> This functionality is not used at this time. 
